title: Looking for ranked 5 team!
body:
Forums are hell to navigate through but i've decided this is where im leaving my thread. 
Im looking for a 5 man team in need of a 5th man. I currently run fill as my que and dont 
mind playing any role. I feel im strongest support(due to my self control) or jungle(due to 
clever plays) my rank isnt braggable but im far beyond the ability of a bronze. I have teamspeak
but can download any voice chat you guys use really. I dont plan on screening teams
but i dont plan on jumping into the first team that offers me a position either. please let
me know i recently quit 10 years of runescaping and plan to fill the void with league!
